    "Out of the population of almost 2000 students, 216 participants were selected through a simple random sampling method.",
    "While 123 (56.9%) participants are male; 88 (40.7); are female.",
    "5 participants (2.3%) did not specify their gender.",
    "Sample Distribution (Demographic profile)",
    "Prior to developing an appropriate questionnaire, an extensive review of existing research was carried out."
